<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230674>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Elbenia fraser sp. n.: habitus of male holotype in dorso-lateral view (A); head in dorsal view (B); male left tegmen in dorsal view (C), stridulatory file on left tegmen in ventral view (D), male abdominal apex in dorsal (E), and lateral (F) views. Scale bars: 1 mm (B, D – F); 5 mm (C)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230674/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

